text: Itheum alboscutellare is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1940. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Itheum alboscutellare. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1940
title: Itheum alboscutellare
